      "message": "Patch Set 1: (1 inline comment)\n\nI'd prefer the comment to be fixed, but it isn't fatal.\n\nMy other main question is how this interacts with http://review.whamcloud.com/4511?  Is this going to introduce another off-by-one bug, or is it fixing one?  From the comment it would seem that this is only a cosmetic issue, but I don't see all of the places that opd_pre_last_created is used being updated.",
