        "username": "bzzz"
      },
      "date": "2012-11-28 09:26:15.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Looks good to me, approved\n\nfine with me.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
